            "textblock": "The study is designed to observe the clinical outcomes of heart failure patients treated\n      with C-Pulse\u00ae System in the usual manner and according to the approved indications and\n      contraindications."
        }, 
        "brief_title": "C-Pulse\u00ae System European Multicenter Study", 
